hondura seek pl-480 vessel for bulk wheat hondura will tender april 13 under public law 480 for u.s. and non-u.s. flag vessel to deliv approxim 52,500 tonn of variou wheat in bulk , an agent for the countri said . the agent said deliveri of northern spring/dn wheat will includ layday of juli 1-10 for 7,500-9,500 tonn , august 1-10 for 8,000-10,000 tonn , and septemb 15-25 for 12,500-14,500 tonn . deliveri of hard red winter wheat will have layday of june 20-30 for 5,000-7,000 tonn , juli 15-25 for 6,500-8,500 tonn , and septemb 15-25 for 7,000-9,000 tonn . offer are due by 1200 hr edt , april 13 , and will remain valid until the close of busi april 14 , the agent said .